{"tid":1309693,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"辛灝年:被高喊了三十年的，和平理性非暴力，應該要終止了","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T10:17:20.000Z","uid":131782,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53d80b3e0606face9c9e202ba87533dbce410cf9","tid":1309693,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">非分化,只係覺得佢講得幾有道理,64唔止係對中國人嘅教訓,仲係教埋香港人,和理非已經不能令中國或者港共作出回應了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uxLc0tQp2qU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuxLc0tQp2qU&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=dc67abb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uxLc0tQp2qU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">42:50</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原因一:<br />\n對抗香港同對抗中共一樣,我哋只要有少少反抗,政府就開始將<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非用嚟將我哋嘅反抗壓迫,咁樣嘅話就只會令政府,自由自在地繼續用政權暴力打壓我哋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原因二:<br />\n六四帶比我哋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">血的教訓</span></strong></span>就係,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和平理性非暴力只會麻痺我哋抗爭嘅神經,削減我哋應有嘅反抗精神。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後，並唔係叫大家唔好做和理非，只係想睇下會唔會有多啲人覺悟</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">和理為盾，勇武為矛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化,不割蓆,不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油"},{"pid":"2ce64441557b6e7cb2a7eb9e344883b43ba056d2","tid":1309693,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}